						<p>Fragment. Contains a portion of the <hi rend="italic">mēykīrtti</hi> of the king. Mentions Neṉmalināḍu (a sub-division) of Arumoḻidēva-vaḷanāḍu. Mentions a certain Śrī Tattaṉ. Other details are lost.</p>						

